00:00:03.245 --> 00:00:07.190
Welcome to nishamadhulika.com.

00:00:07.772 --> 00:00:15.133
A bowl of tomato soup before meal increases both taste of food and hunger.

00:00:15.580 --> 00:00:19.209
Today, we will prepare mix-vegetable tomato soup.

00:00:19.505 --> 00:00:20.356
Let us see.

00:00:20.539 --> 00:00:24.987
What are the ingredients required to prepare the vegetable tomato soup.

00:00:25.687 --> 00:00:27.219
Tomato - 500 grams

00:00:27.521 --> 00:00:28.951
Take to 4-5 tomatoes

00:00:29.253 --> 00:00:30.968
Ginger - A piece of 1 inch.

00:00:31.628 --> 00:00:33.750
1 Carrot - Finely chopped.

00:00:34.092 --> 00:00:36.752
Broccoli - Finely chopped

00:00:37.414 --> 00:00:39.072
Cream - 2 tablespoonful.

00:00:39.756 --> 00:00:42.553
Coriander - 2 tablespoonful (finely chopped).

00:00:43.190 --> 00:00:44.896
Cornflour - 1 tablespoonful.

00:00:45.532 --> 00:00:47.422
Butter - 1 tablespoonful.

00:00:48.178 --> 00:00:49.973
Salt - 1 teaspoonful.

00:00:50.570 --> 00:00:54.382
Black Pepper - ¼  teaspoonful.

00:00:55.177 --> 00:00:57.108
Black salt - ¼ teaspoonful.

00:00:57.275 --> 00:01:07.889
Chop ginger and  tomatoes into large pieces and make a thin paste of it.

00:01:08.931 --> 00:01:11.884
The paste of ginger and tomato is ready

00:01:12.228 --> 00:01:13.593
We will boil the paste now.

00:01:20.871 --> 00:01:23.206
Take the paste of tomato in a tumbler.

00:01:25.932 --> 00:01:27.854
Add half or ¼ cup of water in it.

00:01:29.874 --> 00:01:38.826
We will boil it till its colour changes.

00:01:39.264 --> 00:01:41.647
It will take 7-8 minutes

00:01:41.870 --> 00:01:46.732
Let’s prepare the cornflour in the meantime.

00:01:47.050 --> 00:01:48.606
We will also make the vegetables soft.

00:01:50.117 --> 00:01:51.960
Take cornflour in a bowl.

00:01:52.112 --> 00:01:56.551
Add water and mix it till it becomes smooth.

00:01:57.061 --> 00:01:59.896
If we will add all the water at the same time.

00:02:00.358 --> 00:02:02.740
It will be difficult to make it smooth

00:02:08.143 --> 00:02:11.504
Add half cup of water in it and keep it aside.

00:02:12.435 --> 00:02:18.925
Tomatoes are boiled now. Filter these after some time.

00:02:20.801 --> 00:02:23.508
Make the vegetables soft in butter.

00:02:23.763 --> 00:02:32.199
Heat the pan and take 1 or 2 spoons of butter in it.

00:02:38.667 --> 00:02:40.367
Heat the butter till it melts.

00:02:49.153 --> 00:02:51.140
Add broccoli and carrot in butter.

00:02:51.889 --> 00:02:54.390
Heat these vegetable till these become soft.

00:02:55.885 --> 00:03:01.781
You can add vegetables like cauliflower, beans or capsicum.

00:03:02.472 --> 00:03:06.634
According to your choice or availability.

00:03:07.682 --> 00:03:11.956
Chop them finely and make them soft similarly.

00:03:13.070 --> 00:03:16.581
Vegetables have turned crispy and soft.

00:03:18.607 --> 00:03:19.783
Cover the pan with a lid.

00:03:21.262 --> 00:03:23.660
Let’s filter tomatoes in the meantime

00:03:24.240 --> 00:03:30.897
We can also cut the tomato and boil it in the same way.

00:03:31.691 --> 00:03:36.983
It can be prepared by any one of the way.

00:03:38.398 --> 00:03:42.633
Press the tomatoes to take out the juice.

00:03:51.706 --> 00:03:53.303
Add vegetables in it.

00:03:54.891 --> 00:03:56.416
Also add 3 cups of water in it.

00:04:18.679 --> 00:04:22.881
Mix cornflour in it.

00:04:32.321 --> 00:04:36.173
Boil it again for 5-6 minutes.

00:04:37.548 --> 00:04:42.823
Add salt, black pepper and black salt in it.

00:04:53.000 --> 00:04:55.534
Cover it with a lid.

00:04:57.903 --> 00:05:01.327
We will boil it again for 4-5 minutes.

00:05:02.100 --> 00:05:04.718
Boil the soup in mid-flame now.

00:05:05.300 --> 00:05:06.847
(After 4-5 mins)

00:05:07.081 --> 00:05:10.009
The soup is now ready.

00:05:10.384 --> 00:05:11.336
Turn off the burner now.

00:05:23.939 --> 00:05:25.933
Garnish it with coriander.

00:05:30.310 --> 00:05:35.393
We can also garnish it with 1-2 teaspoonful of cream in it.

00:05:41.734 --> 00:05:42.950
Tomato soup is now ready.

